{"lastModified":1775206915460,"uri":"c::50593508610::vessel::bedf7430-067d-11f1-9942-d7bca84f5f72","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Italy\n\nMIMAY is Alkadia's pilot project. The schooner, purchased in 2022, was completely redesigned and, over the course of three years, rebuilt from the keel up using time-honored Italian naval techniques. The rebuilding process was completed in every part except the engine, which is currently still a classic diesel, pending the development and patenting with the University of a new, totally green propulsion system, designed by Alkadia. Today, Mimay is a vintage vessel, a unique blend of ancient and futuristic.","blueprint":{"name":"MIMAY","images":["/media/media::image::c::50593508610::vessel::bedf7430-067d-11f1-9942-d7bca84f5f72::assets::dae7acf0-1c9f-11f1-a622-e9d989858b83/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::50593508610::vessel::bedf7430-067d-11f1-9942-d7bca84f5f72::assets::dae737c0-1c9f-11f1-a622-e9d989858b83/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::50593508610::vessel::bedf7430-067d-11f1-9942-d7bca84f5f72::assets::dae6e9a1-1c9f-11f1-a622-e9d989858b83/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::50593508610::vessel::bedf7430-067d-11f1-9942-d7bca84f5f72::assets::daeaba30-1c9f-11f1-a622-e9d989858b83/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::50593508610::vessel::bedf7430-067d-11f1-9942-d7bca84f5f72::assets::dae75ed0-1c9f-11f1-a622-e9d989858b83/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::50593508610::vessel::bedf7430-067d-11f1-9942-d7bca84f5f72::assets::daeb5671-1c9f-11f1-a622-e9d989858b83/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::50593508610::vessel::bedf7430-067d-11f1-9942-d7bca84f5f72::assets::dae90c80-1c9f-11f1-a622-e9d989858b83/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::50593508610::vessel::bedf7430-067d-11f1-9942-d7bca84f5f72::assets::dae69b80-1c9f-11f1-a622-e9d989858b83/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::50593508610::vessel::bedf7430-067d-11f1-9942-d7bca84f5f72::assets::dae9a8c0-1c9f-11f1-a622-e9d989858b8